Yeah, so in the demo, the slides where I was showing like what the tidy models code would

00:22:12.239 --> 00:22:17.920
look like and then what the code would look like with a bunch of different engines, that

00:22:18.959 --> 00:22:22.959
code is what we would use to fit a linear regression in tidy models.

00:22:23.199 --> 00:22:27.280
And the code looks super similar to do the same for logistic regression.

