I spoke a little bit to how tidy models is extensible.

00:22:47.680 --> 00:22:50.079
Any developer can add on to tidy models.

00:22:50.400 --> 00:23:00.319
We try to make it really straightforward to incorporate methods that further the ecosystem

00:23:00.319 --> 00:23:04.079
without us having to kind of give it a thumbs up.

00:23:04.640 --> 00:23:12.160
One of the there's like an ecosystem of packages that was developed by somebody external to our

