It's called model time.

00:23:14.319 --> 00:23:19.920
And model time, again, it's from a user in the community.

00:23:19.920 --> 00:23:26.640
And there's all sorts of options to working with time series models using tidy models

00:23:26.640 --> 00:23:27.520
through that package.

